February 29,2020.

The 7th day of the 2nd Lunar Month.

Wuhan is closed for thirty-eight days.

The Gate of Heaven is sealed for thirty-seven days.

The weather's unpredictable.

At noon, Dafangbo did turn dumplings, taste no worse than buy, said very satisfied with their craft. In the evening, he and Chengxuan Buzhengshi went out to pick up the food they had ordered online, only to find that the street in front of the House had been completely blocked off. I can only stand on Tiptoe, through the wall and each other to reach, to bring back food. Two bags of rice, a few stubs of cabbage and cabbage, a few roots of lettuce and cucumber, and a bag of tomatoes and steamed bread, garlic sprouts, carrots and potatoes no delivery tomorrow. Uncle said he can manage it for at least a week. Coincidentally, the food delivery was actually a relative, asked him if he needed volunteers, he said forget it, too tired, he has a big head, and miscellaneous busy to one or two every day. I had to say, "take care. ".
